WEBVTT

00:07.640 --> 00:08.960
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:37.160 --> 01:39.680
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

01:46.040 --> 01:46.960
‎TAIJI HALL

01:47.040 --> 01:49.520
Zhu Yong is backed by the Grand Princess.

01:49.600 --> 01:52.080
Now, in the Imperial Guard Office,
he's a favorite.

01:52.160 --> 01:54.680
The Imperial Guard Office
arrests anyone at will.

01:54.760 --> 01:56.080
Even Mr. Deng…

02:01.480 --> 02:03.680
His Majesty is here.

02:07.080 --> 02:09.039
‎DILIGENT AND VIRTUOUS

02:20.960 --> 02:22.240
Kneel.

02:26.480 --> 02:28.520
-Greetings, Your Majesty.
-Greetings, Your Majesty.

02:28.600 --> 02:30.680
-Greetings, Your Highness.
-Greetings, Your Highness.

02:31.280 --> 02:32.560
Bow.

02:35.960 --> 02:37.400
You may rise.

02:37.480 --> 02:39.800
-Thank you, Your Majesty.
-Thank you, Your Majesty.

02:43.640 --> 02:46.600
Your Highness, I request to go to Huzhou

02:46.680 --> 02:48.400
for the summer flood corruption case.

02:49.760 --> 02:52.200
-What?
-He wants to investigate?

02:52.800 --> 02:54.760
This is a serious case.

02:54.840 --> 02:57.200
The Commandant of Justice,
the Minister of Revenue,

02:57.280 --> 02:59.280
and the Imperial Guard Office
will co-investigate.

03:00.040 --> 03:01.400
Mr. Deng, make the arrangements.

03:05.120 --> 03:06.240
Yes.

03:10.520 --> 03:11.360
XIE'S MANSION

03:11.440 --> 03:14.040
Her Highness had the Imperial Guard Office
cooperate with Mr. Deng

03:14.120 --> 03:15.240
instead of being arbitrary.

03:15.320 --> 03:18.240
And Mr. Deng responded to Her Highness.

03:18.320 --> 03:22.760
Doesn't that mean
he accepts her political interference?

03:25.320 --> 03:26.680
How do I know what she thinks?

03:29.360 --> 03:32.880
Don't you always say
Chu Zhao is just like you?

03:33.440 --> 03:36.000
How do you not know what she thinks?

03:38.640 --> 03:39.680
Fine.

03:40.800 --> 03:43.360
Then I will think about it.

03:49.560 --> 03:52.000
Last night, she visited Mr. Deng.

03:52.840 --> 03:56.960
I thought they would fall out
and break up.

03:59.800 --> 04:03.360
Unexpectedly, they put on an act together.

04:04.320 --> 04:07.000
An act? For whom?

04:07.080 --> 04:09.000
Me, of course.

04:09.840 --> 04:11.880
In case my clan has sole dominance

04:11.960 --> 04:13.960
and seizes power from His Majesty,

04:14.480 --> 04:16.240
she even supports Mr. Deng

04:16.320 --> 04:18.680
to maintain tripartite balance
within the court.

04:19.560 --> 04:20.839
She's clever.

04:22.320 --> 04:23.600
But sadly, she's too soft-hearted.

04:24.520 --> 04:26.080
She wants a stable court.

04:26.680 --> 04:28.320
Then I will let her know

04:29.160 --> 04:31.920
kindness can't survive in this world.

05:01.920 --> 05:04.120
Have Yu Shang send this
to the Northern Desert.

05:04.200 --> 05:08.480
It's been years since Zhong Changrong
guarded Xinggu Pass.

05:08.560 --> 05:09.400
KILL ZHONG CHANGRONG AT XINGGU PASS

05:09.480 --> 05:11.240
He should rest.

05:11.320 --> 05:13.320
If Xinggu Pass is invaded…

05:13.400 --> 05:16.960
So… we'll have Liang Qiang prepare early.

05:31.240 --> 05:33.280
Greetings, Your Majesty.

05:34.160 --> 05:35.560
You're back, Qi Bo.

05:35.640 --> 05:36.720
You're just in time.

05:36.800 --> 05:39.960
The provisions you brought back
last time are running out.

05:40.040 --> 05:40.920
Go get some more.

05:41.680 --> 05:42.920
Already?

05:43.000 --> 05:45.360
We have three contingents.

05:45.440 --> 05:47.040
They're certainly consumed quickly.

05:47.800 --> 05:48.800
Three?

05:49.320 --> 05:51.520
The Eldest Prince is in the rear,

05:52.200 --> 05:54.480
but he still needs our provisions.

05:54.560 --> 05:56.960
My son is securing the rear.

05:57.520 --> 05:59.400
He must be well-fed.

06:03.480 --> 06:04.880
Don't worry.

06:05.400 --> 06:08.160
I'll get the provisions as soon as I can.

06:10.160 --> 06:15.000
This time, I've brought you a transaction

06:15.720 --> 06:17.840
that is very beneficial.

06:27.800 --> 06:29.920
KILL ZHONG CHANGRONG AT XINGGU PASS

06:31.200 --> 06:34.080
Interesting. How interesting.

06:35.520 --> 06:42.400
Xie Yanfang wants me to kill
Zhong Changrong at Xinggu Pass.

06:44.120 --> 06:49.440
Xiao Xun wants my army to pass Xiaonan.

06:51.480 --> 06:55.720
These two idiots both want to court me.

06:56.320 --> 06:57.280
All right.

06:57.360 --> 07:00.840
Then I will fulfill their wishes.

07:01.520 --> 07:02.800
Your Majesty is wise.

07:02.880 --> 07:05.360
Chu Ling is dead.
The State of Chu has civil strife.

07:05.960 --> 07:08.360
This is exactly our moment.

07:10.360 --> 07:12.880
Issue my order. Send a troop of soldiers.

07:13.920 --> 07:16.000
I'll show them

07:17.440 --> 07:19.400
how I can benefit

07:23.800 --> 07:25.160
from their own infighting.

07:25.240 --> 07:29.600
XINGGU PASS

07:44.440 --> 07:46.520
Don't move, General Liang.

07:49.000 --> 07:51.440
-What do you want?
-Don't be nervous.

07:52.280 --> 07:54.480
The Northern Desert troops
are just passing by.

07:57.520 --> 07:58.520
This is treason!

07:59.480 --> 08:01.600
It isn't.

08:01.680 --> 08:04.080
It's just a deal.

08:05.040 --> 08:06.760
Mr. Xie passed an order.

08:06.840 --> 08:08.360
"Their troops need a victory.

08:09.640 --> 08:13.520
And the victory we give them
will have no impact on our war situation."

08:14.440 --> 08:18.320
Does Mr. Xie know what will happen?

08:18.400 --> 08:22.560
He said the Northern Desert King
would send troops.

08:23.240 --> 08:26.160
Zhong Changrong would die at Xinggu Pass.

08:26.240 --> 08:27.360
Then…

08:27.440 --> 08:30.320
His position will be yours.

08:31.400 --> 08:34.520
General Liang, all you need to do
is stand here

08:34.600 --> 08:37.240
and pretend you didn't see anything.

09:01.800 --> 09:03.240
XINGGU PASS

09:03.320 --> 09:05.120
CHANGPING PASS

09:05.200 --> 09:11.120
CHANGPING PASS

09:16.000 --> 09:19.720
General, the enemy king
decamped and disappeared.

09:20.440 --> 09:25.960
So far, no beacon smoke has been seen
throughout Yunzhong.

09:27.360 --> 09:28.800
Could they be lying in ambush?

09:31.880 --> 09:35.480
From their former encampment to Yunzhong,

09:36.200 --> 09:40.520
there aren't valleys or depressions
for such a large army to hide.

09:40.600 --> 09:42.160
Report!

09:43.200 --> 09:44.120
Raid on Xinggu Pass!

09:48.280 --> 09:49.840
Zhong is just patrolling there.

09:49.920 --> 09:53.680
But… General Zhong's route
is a military secret.

09:54.440 --> 09:56.440
-Call up 500 soldiers. We'll go.
-Yes.

10:01.200 --> 10:03.080
General, this raid is so precise.

10:03.160 --> 10:04.640
Someone must have leaked our route.

10:04.720 --> 10:06.320
Do they think they can invade us this way?

10:06.400 --> 10:07.960
What a pipe dream!

10:08.800 --> 10:11.200
I'm their target.

10:33.760 --> 10:35.080
General Liang,

10:35.160 --> 10:37.560
the Northern Desert troops passed
through your guarding area.

10:38.160 --> 10:40.320
However perfectly we carry out this plan,

10:40.400 --> 10:42.760
Zhong Changrong will suspect you.

10:43.880 --> 10:45.520
When he gets to the bottom,

10:45.600 --> 10:48.640
by then, even if someone protects you,

10:48.720 --> 10:51.800
you'll have to work in the labor camp
as a guilty person.

10:51.880 --> 10:55.640
Your clan won't be able to rise again.

11:10.320 --> 11:11.360
So,

11:12.440 --> 11:14.120
what do you want me to do?

11:14.720 --> 11:16.640
You have to kill all those enemies.

11:16.720 --> 11:20.400
Because Zhong Changrong's followers
must witness that scene

11:20.480 --> 11:22.120
of valor and tragedy.

11:22.200 --> 11:25.360
Right now, a squad of several hundred men
is patrolling not far away.

11:27.680 --> 11:29.240
Shoot this whistling arrow.

11:29.320 --> 11:31.880
Our men will lure that squad over to you.

11:31.960 --> 11:34.640
That way, your bravery will be witnessed,

11:35.240 --> 11:37.560
and you won't die while outnumbered.

11:38.880 --> 11:43.400
General Liang, after you take over
the frontier command,

11:43.480 --> 11:46.360
you'll bring glory to the state
and fortune to people.

11:46.440 --> 11:49.720
Your name will go down in history.

11:55.120 --> 11:57.840
Charge!

12:01.640 --> 12:03.760
You should be guarding Xinggu Pass.
Why are you here?

12:04.360 --> 12:07.320
I was surveying nearby terrain
and passed by.

12:07.880 --> 12:10.400
Another squad is coming over.
Hold on, General Zhong.

13:15.760 --> 13:17.400
Take him back! Keep him alive!

13:17.480 --> 13:18.760
-Yes.
-Mr. Zhong.

13:21.400 --> 13:25.040
Hurry. Take men to defend Xinggu Pass.

13:25.680 --> 13:27.760
Mr. Zhong. Mr. Zhong.

13:27.840 --> 13:30.960
-Light a smoke signal. Full-scale alert!
-Yes.

13:31.040 --> 13:33.360
‎XINGGU PASS

13:42.200 --> 13:43.160
How's General?

13:44.280 --> 13:45.560
His vital organs aren't injured,

13:46.160 --> 13:47.360
but he's bleeding seriously.

13:47.960 --> 13:48.880
I'm afraid…

13:50.760 --> 13:52.560
Keep him alive, or I'll kill you.

13:52.640 --> 13:56.040
-Yes. I'll do my best.
-General.

13:56.120 --> 13:58.360
General. Wangcheng is lost.

14:02.680 --> 14:03.800
It's a trap.

14:32.760 --> 14:33.960
Did you have a nightmare?

14:35.440 --> 14:37.520
Shall I take you back for some rest?

14:43.240 --> 14:45.040
Your Highness, urgent frontier report.

14:45.120 --> 14:47.200
Wangcheng is lost.
General Zhong is badly injured.

14:50.280 --> 14:51.920
URGENT DISPATCH FROM YUNZHONG

14:59.440 --> 15:01.960
-How is Jiu doing?
-We don't know the specifics.

15:05.640 --> 15:07.120
Don't worry too much.

15:07.200 --> 15:09.760
When Jiu is there,
the frontier won't fall.

15:15.000 --> 15:16.720
WANGCHENG LOST. GENERAL ZHONG WOUNDED.
URGENT REQUEST FOR TROOPS AND PROVISIONS.

15:17.800 --> 15:21.080
The report only says enemy troops
broke through Xinggu Pass.

15:21.160 --> 15:22.720
Not a word is about Liang Qiang.

15:23.360 --> 15:25.560
He's the general guarding Xinggu Pass.

15:25.640 --> 15:26.680
In such a big case,

15:27.360 --> 15:29.080
his condition should be reported,

15:29.160 --> 15:30.840
whether he's dead or missing.

15:32.360 --> 15:35.880
Unless he's highly suspicious

15:36.800 --> 15:38.080
and many people are involved.

15:38.960 --> 15:41.680
So, at this crucial point,
it must be set aside

15:41.760 --> 15:43.240
to avoid shaking the morale.

15:48.240 --> 15:49.920
Wangcheng is strategically vital!

15:50.680 --> 15:54.080
Once it's lost, Yunzhong will be in peril!

15:54.160 --> 15:57.320
If Yunzhong is lost,

15:57.400 --> 15:59.400
our state will be in peril!

15:59.480 --> 16:00.600
That's right.

16:00.680 --> 16:02.960
If Yunzhong is lost, we will be in danger.

16:05.640 --> 16:07.680
Xie Yanlai bragged that he would

16:07.760 --> 16:09.760
kill the Northern Desert King,

16:09.840 --> 16:12.160
but now, he can't even
defend the frontier.

16:12.240 --> 16:13.280
He must be severely punished.

16:13.920 --> 16:14.840
Yes.

16:14.920 --> 16:18.440
He lost one city,
then he may lose another.

16:18.520 --> 16:22.840
How many cities are there at the frontier?

16:22.920 --> 16:27.360
How could Your Highness trust
such an impetuous man?

16:28.080 --> 16:30.240
Yeah. Things can't go on like this.

16:31.560 --> 16:32.520
Ministers,

16:33.560 --> 16:36.200
at this point, what's the use of arguing?

16:39.080 --> 16:41.800
The Northern Desert King sent a message,

16:42.400 --> 16:44.040
asking for peace talks.

16:44.120 --> 16:47.160
I think we should avoid
direct confrontation.

16:48.920 --> 16:50.280
We will

16:52.080 --> 16:53.520
never accept peace talks.

17:05.720 --> 17:06.839
Never?

17:08.760 --> 17:10.359
So will the war continue?

17:11.440 --> 17:13.480
Will we ignore the people in Wangcheng?

17:13.560 --> 17:17.480
The King wants friendly relations
and territorial concessions.

17:18.400 --> 17:19.599
Is this a peace offer?

17:19.680 --> 17:21.280
This is a humiliation.

17:22.119 --> 17:24.760
Countless soldiers shouldn't die in vain.

17:24.839 --> 17:27.280
My father's decade-long persistence
shouldn't be wasted.

17:27.359 --> 17:28.880
Wangcheng is lost,

17:28.960 --> 17:30.880
but Your Highness is still so stubborn.

17:30.960 --> 17:33.000
What will people think of you?

17:34.200 --> 17:36.040
Why don't you leave the court

17:37.040 --> 17:38.680
and let me handle this?

17:39.480 --> 17:41.520
Mr. Deng, are you saying

17:41.600 --> 17:44.200
I am to blame for the error
of the frontier troops?

17:45.560 --> 17:47.240
Xie Yanlai serves you.

17:48.000 --> 17:50.720
In that case, you can't shirk the blame.

17:51.360 --> 17:53.480
When I was in charge,
the frontier was safe.

17:54.200 --> 17:56.080
After the supervisors you sent there,

17:56.680 --> 17:59.000
especially Liang Qiang you favor,

17:59.080 --> 18:01.960
failed their duties,
the enemies managed to break in.

18:05.880 --> 18:08.120
Your Highness learned to shift blame.

18:09.080 --> 18:10.120
I would rather say,

18:10.200 --> 18:13.040
I interfered so late

18:13.120 --> 18:15.920
that frontier troops were too corrupt
to be mended.

18:16.000 --> 18:17.840
Even when Liang Qiang was favored,

18:18.880 --> 18:21.080
he couldn't reverse the decline!

18:21.920 --> 18:23.400
Mr. Deng,

18:24.240 --> 18:26.480
who do you think will benefit

18:26.560 --> 18:29.560
from the failure of frontier troops
and the loss of a city?

18:35.120 --> 18:37.000
You don't think

18:37.800 --> 18:40.840
I used the failure of the troops
and the suffering of the people

18:41.560 --> 18:44.440
to force you out of the court, do you?

18:45.640 --> 18:48.640
Chu Zhao, you aren't worthy.

18:49.400 --> 18:51.720
You always claim
you prioritize self-interest.

18:51.800 --> 18:54.400
I thought you were
just saying that for fun.

18:54.480 --> 18:58.320
What a surprise.
You really dared to do that.

18:59.080 --> 19:00.160
Xiaoman.

19:11.040 --> 19:13.160
These are your letters
with frontier troops,

19:13.240 --> 19:14.680
including private letters.

19:19.120 --> 19:22.960
Chu Zhao, how dare you pry
into my privacy?

19:23.040 --> 19:24.720
I just did. So what?

19:24.800 --> 19:26.840
You supervise by late Emperor's order.

19:26.920 --> 19:28.920
I protect the state by his order.

19:29.520 --> 19:31.640
So, I must know anything that involves

19:32.240 --> 19:33.720
our state affairs.

19:35.000 --> 19:37.240
Take out Mr. Deng's letters
to and from Liang Qiang

19:37.960 --> 19:41.560
and his letters with other ministers
where they plotted to depose me.

19:41.640 --> 19:42.640
Yes.

19:42.720 --> 19:43.600
YOUR ORIGIN IS NO OBSTACLE. XINGGU PASS
NEEDS YOUR TALENT. JUST GO. BY DENG YI

19:50.440 --> 19:51.440
Liang Qiang said

19:52.240 --> 19:54.240
his transfer to Xinggu Pass was improper.

19:55.680 --> 19:56.600
You said

19:57.520 --> 20:00.560
he could just go ahead
and you would take responsibility

20:01.240 --> 20:03.040
if anything went wrong.

20:04.360 --> 20:06.560
Liang Qiang did write me this letter.

20:07.080 --> 20:10.040
Then I replied like that. What's wrong?

20:10.120 --> 20:12.680
A frontier general knew it was improper.

20:14.400 --> 20:16.800
And a civil official like you,
far back in the Capital,

20:17.440 --> 20:20.680
insisted on meddling in military affairs.

20:24.360 --> 20:25.280
So?

20:26.440 --> 20:29.480
So, you won't come to the court
for a while.

20:30.080 --> 20:31.840
Go back home and reflect on yourself.

20:40.960 --> 20:41.880
Good.

20:44.040 --> 20:45.040
Very good.

20:46.720 --> 20:49.840
Let me see if you can get what you desire

20:50.760 --> 20:53.320
when I'm away from the court.

20:54.000 --> 20:56.840
Xiaoman, send him back home.

20:56.920 --> 20:58.720
Yes, Your Highness.

21:24.840 --> 21:25.720
Mr. Deng,

21:27.080 --> 21:28.560
how have you been?

21:30.440 --> 21:34.200
Mr. Xie, to what do I owe this pleasure?

21:35.040 --> 21:37.080
I'm here to apologize.

21:38.920 --> 21:40.600
You took the blame

21:41.640 --> 21:43.400
for the loss of Wangcheng.

21:44.440 --> 21:46.920
I sent the message to the Northern Desert

21:47.000 --> 21:50.480
and I asked Liang Qiang to defect.

21:51.200 --> 21:53.240
As for why the enemies
passed through Xiaonan

21:53.320 --> 21:55.040
to attack Wangcheng…

21:56.520 --> 21:57.440
I need not say,

21:58.680 --> 22:00.960
for you know who did that.

22:01.560 --> 22:02.680
Xie Yanfang!

22:05.240 --> 22:06.640
How could you do this

22:06.720 --> 22:08.920
to frontier troops and civilians
at Wangcheng?

22:09.600 --> 22:11.800
They are people of our state.

22:12.520 --> 22:14.200
They'll die a worthy death

22:16.800 --> 22:18.360
to sacrifice for their state.

22:19.720 --> 22:21.560
You can go and turn me in.

22:22.160 --> 22:23.200
However,

22:23.920 --> 22:25.920
who would believe
your one-sided statement?

22:40.640 --> 22:41.480
Fine.

22:43.560 --> 22:48.640
I'll wait and see
what exactly you are up to.

22:53.200 --> 22:54.880
Well, it's getting late.

22:56.840 --> 22:58.120
I'll take my leave.

23:07.120 --> 23:08.720
I do hope

23:09.840 --> 23:13.600
I can see you again at the court.

23:49.520 --> 23:50.960
Thinking about what happened?

23:56.480 --> 23:58.320
Be seated, Mr. Xie.

24:01.920 --> 24:03.600
I thought hard, but I don't get it.

24:04.280 --> 24:06.680
If he simply wanted me
to withdraw from the court,

24:06.760 --> 24:10.760
why did he sacrifice the frontier
and civilians in Wangcheng?

24:10.840 --> 24:12.480
This isn't Deng Yi's style.

24:12.560 --> 24:16.760
Your Highness,
Mr. Deng's desire has never changed.

24:16.840 --> 24:20.320
I have proof
that Liang Qiang serves Mr. Deng.

24:21.600 --> 24:25.040
So you think he wants
to command frontier troops?

24:29.960 --> 24:33.400
So, he wanted Mr. Zhong dead in this raid,

24:34.000 --> 24:36.680
then Liang Qiang would turn the tide
and take command.

24:37.280 --> 24:38.560
To be honest,

24:39.360 --> 24:41.200
it has something to do with Yanlai.

24:42.440 --> 24:44.000
I guess Mr. Deng believed

24:44.080 --> 24:47.040
Yanlai dared to make that military pledge

24:47.680 --> 24:50.120
because my whole clan backed him up.

24:51.320 --> 24:53.600
He couldn't bear to see
military power slip.

24:53.680 --> 24:56.720
That's why he took
desperate risks at any cost.

24:58.360 --> 24:59.760
As for Wangcheng…

25:01.080 --> 25:04.080
We are not certain if he was behind that.

25:05.040 --> 25:06.280
Or maybe

25:07.040 --> 25:08.440
that was merely an accident.

25:09.400 --> 25:11.360
After all, the tides of war always change.

25:11.440 --> 25:14.160
One false move
may lead to the loss of a city.

25:18.320 --> 25:20.160
I don't usually get along with Mr. Deng,

25:20.960 --> 25:25.040
but I refuse to believe
he would collude with our enemies.

25:26.280 --> 25:28.000
Now, the situation is complicated.

25:28.080 --> 25:32.200
For the moment,
our priority is to stabilize the court.

25:36.680 --> 25:37.640
I know.

25:38.720 --> 25:40.960
He was under house arrest

25:41.040 --> 25:42.960
because he argued with me
on whether to have

25:43.840 --> 25:44.960
peace talks.

25:45.920 --> 25:47.400
As for how we should handle him…

25:48.000 --> 25:51.640
After we take back Wangcheng
and uncover the truth, we'll know.

25:52.440 --> 25:54.040
Don't worry too much.

25:54.640 --> 25:58.920
The sudden loss of Wangcheng
was truly horrifying.

25:59.000 --> 26:02.920
Fortunately, Yunzhong led all units
to heavily guard it

26:03.000 --> 26:05.640
and fought the invaders.

26:05.720 --> 26:07.920
Those invaders failed to advance further.

26:10.480 --> 26:12.560
I have faith in frontier troops.

26:13.200 --> 26:14.760
But how about people in Wangcheng?

26:16.280 --> 26:17.920
If we reject peace talks,

26:18.000 --> 26:20.120
the enemies will threaten us
with a massacre.

26:22.080 --> 26:25.400
Peace talks start with talks.

26:25.480 --> 26:29.040
In that case,
we'll have time to negotiate.

26:30.640 --> 26:31.600
Rest assured.

26:31.680 --> 26:38.280
Soon, I will ask relevant ministers
to draft an agenda for you to review.

26:39.600 --> 26:41.000
Thank you, Mr. Xie.

26:42.200 --> 26:43.880
Mr. Deng has been confined.

26:43.960 --> 26:47.200
At this moment, I should step up.

26:48.200 --> 26:51.040
You're truly a blessing for our state.

26:55.320 --> 26:57.840
Don't say that, Your Highness.

27:00.360 --> 27:01.600
In every way,

27:02.920 --> 27:04.120
we're a family.

27:10.440 --> 27:12.000
Tea is good.

27:12.760 --> 27:14.720
But too much tea will upset you.

27:14.800 --> 27:16.560
It's almost lunchtime.

27:17.640 --> 27:20.920
Go have a good lunch with Yu
and get some sleep.

27:21.000 --> 27:25.160
I'm afraid we're going to confront
tough challenges.

27:26.400 --> 27:29.640
I certainly believe
you're tough-minded enough.

27:29.720 --> 27:33.840
But you still need a healthy body.

27:38.760 --> 27:40.160
Don't panic.

27:43.320 --> 27:44.560
You have me.

27:57.400 --> 27:58.640
Le.

27:59.560 --> 28:00.520
Your Highness.

28:00.600 --> 28:03.480
Recently, has Xiao Xun behaved?

28:03.560 --> 28:04.960
Precisely.

28:05.040 --> 28:07.760
For nearly half a year,
he hasn't left his house.

28:07.840 --> 28:09.720
Over the last month,
he has stayed indoors,

28:09.800 --> 28:11.120
making his father's birthday gift.

28:11.720 --> 28:13.360
-Keep watching.
-Yes.

28:19.880 --> 28:21.920
NEED AID URGENTLY.

28:22.000 --> 28:23.760
WANGCHENG LOST. GENERAL ZHONG WOUNDED.
URGENT REQUEST FOR TROOPS AND PROVISIONS.

28:30.920 --> 28:34.320
LONGEVITY SCROLL OF A THOUSAND BLESSINGS

28:46.720 --> 28:48.680
Your Highness, news just came in.

28:48.760 --> 28:50.320
Mr. Deng was escorted out
by the Imperial Guard Office

28:50.400 --> 28:51.320
and then confined in his mansion.

28:51.400 --> 28:52.840
The reason is unknown.

28:52.920 --> 28:55.080
We only know he fought
Her Highness after court.

29:00.480 --> 29:02.800
Your Highness, this might be our chance.

29:03.440 --> 29:05.520
Before I finish my father's gift,

29:06.960 --> 29:09.480
so much has already happened
in the Capital.

29:10.360 --> 29:11.720
But for me,

29:12.760 --> 29:14.680
nothing matters more

29:14.760 --> 29:18.200
than this Scroll of Longevity
for my father.

29:36.760 --> 29:38.400
It's finally done.

29:39.240 --> 29:41.240
I should go visit Mr. Deng.

29:42.240 --> 29:44.280
XIAONAN

29:51.560 --> 29:53.280
How's Xun doing?

29:53.360 --> 29:56.240
Very well. He's been patient.

29:56.320 --> 29:59.640
He has sent your birthday gift
to the Imperial Manufactories.

29:59.720 --> 30:01.720
It will be delivered here
with official gifts.

30:01.800 --> 30:05.240
I had intended to keep the official gifts
outside my prefecture.

30:06.000 --> 30:07.880
Since Xun's gift is among them,

30:09.040 --> 30:10.440
get all those gifts in, then.

30:12.520 --> 30:14.000
Look at this.

30:16.160 --> 30:19.120
WANGCHENG FELL LAST MIDNIGHT. NORTHERN
DESERT TROOPS HEADING FOR YUNZHONG

30:19.800 --> 30:20.800
Wangcheng is lost?

30:22.200 --> 30:24.600
The Northern Desert King
will threaten the court with that city.

30:24.680 --> 30:27.040
For the sake of thousands of civilians,

30:27.120 --> 30:29.040
the court will have to accept peace talks.

30:30.000 --> 30:31.920
But under such circumstances,

30:32.000 --> 30:33.880
if you send troops against the court,

30:33.960 --> 30:35.240
things might backfire.

30:35.840 --> 30:37.800
Threatening with Wangcheng,

30:37.880 --> 30:39.960
those foes will get what they want.

30:40.640 --> 30:42.760
They'll also end the war decently.

30:43.480 --> 30:46.160
For them, that will be a victory.

30:47.280 --> 30:49.000
As for the young emperor,

30:49.080 --> 30:52.280
Chu Zhao, Deng Yi, and Xie Yanfang,

30:53.600 --> 30:56.480
they will lose people's support
as well as their prestige.

30:56.560 --> 30:57.400
By then…

30:57.480 --> 30:59.480
Your prestige will rise greatly.

30:59.560 --> 31:02.880
When you call to arms,
the world will be yours.

31:05.720 --> 31:08.600
‎WANGCHENG NORTH GATE

31:16.120 --> 31:17.560
WANGCHENG

31:23.600 --> 31:24.520
Help them!

31:25.120 --> 31:26.040
Go. Let's help them!

31:28.040 --> 31:29.520
WANGCHENG

31:33.400 --> 31:34.640
Stop.

31:34.720 --> 31:37.040
See how many people here
will have to die for you!

31:37.640 --> 31:39.360
General, what do we do?

31:39.440 --> 31:41.040
Bring it on!

31:43.560 --> 31:45.480
-Retreat.
-General!

31:45.560 --> 31:46.680
I said, retreat!

31:47.880 --> 31:49.080
Losers!

31:49.800 --> 31:50.960
Bring it on!

31:57.720 --> 31:59.840
General, General Zhong is awake.

31:59.920 --> 32:02.360
According to the Army Physician,
he will survive.

32:02.440 --> 32:03.280
Won't you see him?

32:07.720 --> 32:08.720
Glad he won't die.

32:09.920 --> 32:11.640
What about the mission I gave you?

32:11.720 --> 32:14.680
Thirty-six soldiers skilled
in disguise and assassination

32:14.760 --> 32:17.560
and familiar with the enemy's capital
are in position.

32:18.240 --> 32:19.320
As you commend,

32:19.400 --> 32:21.120
all has been kept confidential.

32:22.000 --> 32:23.160
Very good.

32:28.120 --> 32:29.280
Move out.

32:42.480 --> 32:43.920
Wangcheng is strategically vital.

32:44.000 --> 32:45.280
WANGCHENG

32:45.360 --> 32:47.560
Thousands of civilians
are in the hands of enemies.

32:48.360 --> 32:49.800
But Yanlai stays within the camp.

32:51.120 --> 32:52.480
No wonder ministers complain.

32:55.240 --> 32:57.840
A general in war
isn't bound by imperial orders.

32:59.120 --> 33:02.000
-I trust him.
-I trust him too.

33:04.440 --> 33:06.880
So, when the ministers
wanted to replace him,

33:06.960 --> 33:08.200
I didn't approve.

33:08.800 --> 33:12.680
But to be honest, I'm a little worried.

33:12.760 --> 33:14.400
Will he be reckless at this juncture?

33:22.160 --> 33:23.440
Did he really go

33:24.920 --> 33:26.480
to kill the Northern Desert King?

33:30.800 --> 33:32.200
Under such circumstances,

33:32.280 --> 33:34.200
even if Yanlai manages to kill the King,

33:35.080 --> 33:37.120
the Eldest Prince will ascend the throne.

33:39.720 --> 33:41.640
He's fierce and warlike,

33:41.720 --> 33:43.440
but not as far-sighted as his father.

33:44.160 --> 33:47.600
By then, he will invade
in the name of revenge.

33:47.680 --> 33:50.040
His army's morale will soar.

33:50.920 --> 33:52.600
I'm afraid peace talks will be hard.

33:53.480 --> 33:57.640
Is there really no solution
to Wangcheng's problem?

34:00.160 --> 34:01.920
WANGCHENG

34:03.800 --> 34:05.560
In that case,

34:07.520 --> 34:09.920
-I'll have to go to Yunzhong again.
-No.

34:22.440 --> 34:24.920
When I go, I can at least
steady the troops.

34:26.199 --> 34:27.600
I'll go instead.

34:31.280 --> 34:33.000
There's something ministers can do,

34:33.880 --> 34:35.120
but a princess can't.

34:36.600 --> 34:38.440
-You…
-Rest assured.

34:38.520 --> 34:41.360
I will not accept any of their conditions.

34:42.280 --> 34:43.920
Yu is my hope.

34:44.639 --> 34:47.239
I place great hopes on him
and intend to support him.

34:48.440 --> 34:52.280
When he was little, he witnessed
his parents' brutal death.

34:53.560 --> 34:56.719
He barely survived and took the throne.

34:56.800 --> 34:58.240
Then rebellion and invasion came.

34:58.840 --> 35:01.040
If he couldn't be a wise emperor

35:01.800 --> 35:02.800
who expanded his state

35:03.400 --> 35:05.440
and achieved something
beyond his forebears,

35:07.640 --> 35:09.560
it would be unfair to what he suffered.

35:13.640 --> 35:15.680
And accepting peace talks

35:17.080 --> 35:20.280
is a humiliation to someone like me.

35:20.360 --> 35:22.400
Then, what are you going to do?

35:23.160 --> 35:26.720
Will you trade the people
in Wangcheng for victory?

35:30.040 --> 35:31.600
How could you think of me that way?

35:38.840 --> 35:40.400
You broke my heart.

35:42.160 --> 35:45.120
Rejecting peace talks is your idea.

35:45.960 --> 35:47.960
Your reputation is Yu's reputation.

35:48.800 --> 35:50.920
How could I ever abandon people
in Wangcheng?

35:51.880 --> 35:53.840
It's all right that you don't trust me.

35:55.200 --> 35:58.120
You should have faith in what I can do.

36:03.200 --> 36:04.240
That's right.

36:06.200 --> 36:07.920
I have faith in what you can do.

36:30.480 --> 36:31.600
From tomorrow on,

36:33.000 --> 36:35.760
kill a hundred civilians
on the rampart every day

36:36.680 --> 36:39.360
until the State of Chu accepts
all our conditions.

36:40.000 --> 36:41.080
Yes.

36:42.160 --> 36:44.760
Your Majesty! Your Majesty!

36:44.840 --> 36:46.280
JUSTICE HANGS ON HIGH

36:49.280 --> 36:51.960
Aren't you a follower
of the Eldest Prince?

36:52.040 --> 36:54.720
Why are you here
instead of in our capital?

36:54.800 --> 36:58.040
The Eldest Prince… He was killed.

36:58.760 --> 37:00.000
What did you say?

37:09.720 --> 37:12.120
It's something my son always keeps.

37:12.200 --> 37:15.600
Some enemy soldiers invaded
our capital and killed His Highness.

37:16.240 --> 37:19.160
Before His Highness died,
he gave this to me.

37:19.240 --> 37:22.080
I fought my way out
to bring you this news!

37:22.680 --> 37:23.920
You must avenge His Highness!

37:25.760 --> 37:27.200
How dare you curse my son!

37:28.920 --> 37:29.800
Son.

37:30.400 --> 37:32.360
My son. My son!

37:33.440 --> 37:35.760
WANGCHENG

37:35.840 --> 37:36.840
Your Majesty.

37:37.960 --> 37:39.440
Oh my son.

37:44.200 --> 37:47.040
CAPITAL

37:53.040 --> 37:55.840
When Mr. Xie goes, he will succeed.

37:55.920 --> 37:58.320
We must teach those foes a good lesson!

37:58.400 --> 37:59.760
-Yes.
-That's right.

37:59.840 --> 38:00.760
Well said!

38:00.840 --> 38:01.680
Give them a lesson.

38:01.760 --> 38:03.440
-Yes.
-Show them what we can do.

38:03.520 --> 38:06.800
Mr. Xie, we'll entrust you
with frontier affairs.

38:08.120 --> 38:10.120
His Majesty and I believe

38:10.200 --> 38:16.000
you will protect our people
and safeguard our state's dignity.

38:16.080 --> 38:18.440
I will not fail my mission.

38:25.360 --> 38:26.720
Great news!

38:28.520 --> 38:29.840
Great news!

38:30.440 --> 38:32.440
Oh no. Great victory!

38:32.520 --> 38:33.800
Great victory!

38:39.000 --> 38:40.480
Guard General Xie Yanlai

38:41.160 --> 38:42.920
has killed the Eldest Prince
of Northern Desert,

38:43.000 --> 38:44.520
broken into the King's camp,

38:44.600 --> 38:47.440
and caught… caught the King alive!

39:08.600 --> 39:10.960
My son!

39:16.760 --> 39:18.080
Terrific!

39:19.000 --> 39:20.160
He caught the King alive.

39:20.240 --> 39:22.680
‎Great.

39:22.760 --> 39:24.120
‎Yes, indeed.

39:32.080 --> 39:33.360
Great.

39:35.640 --> 39:38.560
Yes. This is great.
